title: WellSky
description: Over 60% of our health is impacted by social determinants of health (SDoH) like access to food, jobs, childcare, and housing. WellSky® Social Care Coordination (formerly Healthify) empowers payers to identify social needs in a member population and coordinate care through a network of community-based partners to optimize quality of care, improve outcomes, lower costs, and increase member satisfaction.
